<plot>Finding Mr. Right is apparently as difficult at 8 as it is at 80. Love Takes charts the places that love takes us and leaves us as we fall in and out of love over a lifetime. The debut film of award winning artist Jeanie Finlay combines documentary DV footage with digital design to explore what we talk about when we talk about love. "Candid, sweet and disquieting" Worldwide Short Film Festival, Toronto.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?344997</url></doc>
